# Audit Logs Directory

This directory contains audit logs for newsletter subscription processing.

## Log Files

- `newsletter-subscriptions.log` - Main audit log for all subscription processing activities
- `issue-deletions.log` - Log of automated issue deletions for compliance

## Retention Policy

Audit logs are retained for compliance and debugging purposes. They contain:
- Timestamps of all processing activities
- Issue numbers and basic metadata
- Processing results (success/failure)
- No sensitive personal information (emails are masked in logs)

## Privacy Notice

These logs are designed to maintain audit trails while protecting user privacy.
Email addresses and personal information are not stored in plain text in these logs.